  "name": "Hunter's Camouflage",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/magic/nature/stealth-hide-beast-eyes-green.webp",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 8th level, you can spend time creating camouflage for yourself. You must have access to fresh mud, dirt, plants, soot, or other naturally occurring materials with which to create your camouflage.</p>\n<p>Once you are camouflaged in this way, you gain bonuses to Dexterity (Stealth) checks made within that environment equal to +1 per minute spent creating the camouflage (maximum of +5). This bonus is doubled while standing still.</p>\n<p>This camouflage lasts up to 1 hour or until you or other affects remove it, such as heavy rain.</p>",
